
Spring IOC
---------------
Containers
 - Core :  BeanFactory(I)
 - J2EE :  ApplicationContext(I) & ConfigurableApplicationContext(I)
 
Basic Purpose of Containers:
- Containers will create instances for POJO classes
- manage life-cycle for POJO classes
- do dependancy injection to POJO classes
	
Diff b/w Core container & J2EE container
	
	
Characterstics of spring.xml file
- must configure dtd or xsd : purpose is to validate spring.xml file using sax parser( will check for wellform-ness and validness)
- always start with <beans > tag
